This product includes a wiki engine (the deterministic vault-writing scripts in
claude_librarian/ — fetch_paper, assemble_paper, assemble_finding, vault_scan,
citation_match, apply_edges, create_stubs, init_vault, lint, log — together with
the page/view templates and the lite-drafter / finding-extractor /
metadata-extractor / finding-linker subagent prompts) that is a reimplementation
borrowing the design of:

    claude-paperloom
    https://github.com/trapoom555/claude-paperloom
