    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

A copy of the Apache License, Version 2.0 may be obtained at:

    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

The additions in claude-librarian — Zotero ingestion and hygiene (pyzotero +
bibtex-updater), the Scholar Inbox source adapter (scholarinboxcli), the async
queue model with wiki-ingested markers, the threads/ synthesis layer, and the
unified `librarian` CLI — are original work licensed under the MIT License (see
LICENSE).
